name: Glass Hearts | Kena Jewelry
description:
Kena Jewelry Glass Hearts.

Buy one for yourself or give your love or love to be a beautiful glass heart.

Give one as an affectionate gift, decorate your desk with them, stick them on your windows (glue not included) the possibilities are endless... Everyone loves glass hearts.

Glass heart is approximately an inch x 1/3 inch. With many jewelry options Kena Fine Jewelry is lovingly handcrafted in the San Francisco Bay Area.
